data.title: My Massage at Ooh La Spa
data.text: I asked the front desk staff at the hotel I was staying who they would recomend for a massage and they told me a new place that just opened called Ooh La Spa. The three ladies I encountered there were very pleasant and friendly. The location was easy for me to find and the massage was very, very relaxing. I would highly recommend this place to anybody visiting. Also the regulars who have not yet discovered it. Submitted by: Nick Lazlo
